# OpenAI API Configuration
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-your-openai-api-key-here

# Firebase/Firestore Configuration
FIRESTORE_DATABASE_ID=your-firestore-database-name
PROJECT_ID=your-gcp-project-id

# Frontend URL for CORS (optional - for local development)
FRONTEND_URL=http://localhost:3000

# Instructions:
# 1. Copy this file to .env: cp .env.example .env (Windows: copy .env.example .env)
# 2. Replace placeholder values with your actual credentials
# 3. Never commit .env to version control
#
# How to obtain these values:
# - OPENAI_API_KEY: Get from https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# - FIRESTORE_DATABASE_ID: Usually "(default)" - check Firebase Console → Firestore Database
# - PROJECT_ID: Your GCP/Firebase project ID from Firebase Console → Project Settings
